# adding user access to k8s cluster using Service account Role ,Role Binding

:one: First create namespace as "users" to centralize all users or Service Accounts
:two: Create secret for this service account to get Token , ca.crt for service account.
:three: Create Role inside namespace you want user to have access to it with privelages you want to give it to him.
:four: Create Role-binding in same namespace of role to bind ServiceAccount with Role.
:five: Run Script add-new-user.sh after customize env variables inside it you will get kube-config file use it to access k8s.
